{"tid":1816761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳豐滿Madam被同事性騷擾 Instagram鬧爆","createTime":"2020-01-08T13:17:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T07:24:16.000Z","uid":255266,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8124fe4de60ad2d5ab58ffe25c58401efa3548e","tid":1816761,"uid":255266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"網傳豐滿Madam被同事性騷擾 Instagram鬧爆<br />\n<br />\n早幾個月，有傳媒直播反修例運動衝突嘅時候，<br />\n<br />\n影到一名身穿白tee嘅便衣女警。<br />\n<br />\n網友見到都cap圖討論呢位咁出眾嘅madam，甚至有傳佢喺IG嘅帳戶追蹤人數，<br />\n<br />\n多過警方開嗰個。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過網路話題嘅嘢，過48小時就會沉底。<br />\n<br />\n但係近期又有人摷到關於呢位Madam嘅新聞。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n有傳呢位叫Katy嘅女警，喺IG限時動態出咗幾個post，<br />\n<br />\n都係鬧爆身邊有人搞事講是非，估佢感情生活，<br />\n<br />\n甚至傳佢亂搞男女關係！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%B1%90%E6%BB%BFmadam%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%80%A7%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-instagram%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86-072521217.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%25BB%25BFmadam%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2580%25A7%25E9%25A8%25B7%25E6%2593%25BE-instagram%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E7%2588%2586-072521217.html&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Ig2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=60440202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E5%82%B3%E8%B1%90%E6%BB%BFmadam%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%80%A7%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE-instagram%E9%AC%A7%E7%88%86-072521217.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q86mwAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq86mwAm.jpg&h=8962acbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9dfeb8d5297b8ace80e670e0a05404c7765352b","tid":1816761,"uid":255266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s